{"tid":2285380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴啟思：基本法104條不僅適用於立法會議員，更重要是包括司法人員","createTime":"2020-11-14T04:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:41:11.000Z","uid":278587,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e53dc9e9dc390730ab0c44adba1da6936db7bef9","tid":2285380,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412850&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=111350f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412850&h=e0662728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412850</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】大律師公會主席戴啟思指，特區政府褫奪四名議員資格，過程中無讓他們辯解，有違法治原則。他又憂慮，法官的任免機制日後亦有機會受影響。基本法委員會委員陳弘毅表示，人大決定具法律效力，今次決定並無額外賦權政府裁決或褫奪議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會就立法會議員的資格作出決定，政府隨即宣布取消四名民主派議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會主席戴啟思指，本地法院無權推翻人大決定，但認為今次決定未有成為具體法律條文；而過程中，政府無給予四人辯解機會，有違法治公平公義原則。<br />\n<br />\n戴啟思：「我們不是關注人大常委會權力，而是關注其影響。由行政長官執行，由行政長官點名四人（喪失資格）即時褫奪其資格。我們很難理解是怎樣的法律，是甚麼法律賦權予行政長官。」<br />\n<br />\n他又憂慮日後任免法官的程序會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n戴啟思：「基本法104條不僅適用於立法會議員，包括其他宣誓人，如主要官員，更重要是包括司法人員，是複雜而漫長過程。如你要按照基本法罷免法官，我們不願看到機制被繞過。」<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會委員陳弘毅指，立法會續任一年，同樣是人大常委會的決定，亦都毋須經本地立法實施，強調人大決定具法律效力。<br />\n<br />\n陳弘毅：「這個人大決定根據中國法律制度，有立法的地位及效力。至於今次亦非賦予特首或政府額外權力去撤銷議員資格，只是確認原有的法律渠道，用以決定某議員是否擁護基本法及效忠特區。」<br />\n<br />\n他指，以選舉主任的決定為取消議員資格依據，是立法會延任產生的特殊情況，認為日後會依照基本法、港區國安法或宣誓及聲明條例處理議員資格。"},{"pid":"dd06518d2fc0906a34931ac4a7fdf1b7aa56dd1e","tid":2285380,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2d411484906705b68eb7ea83295b7b6d4aa106","tid":2285380,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e274c515d6bfe8d8b46c68f8ab121afad0c1346","tid":2285380,"uid":52605,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"法律界離地得好緊要<br />\n驚燒到自己嗰疊先喺喉嚨發出蚊滋咁細聲"},{"pid":"c3bfa417d1e6b251714f6dab516ea4eca4fb5fc6","tid":2285380,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1996da67cdf74455b50c9d67e09af7ef1df816b","tid":2285380,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:06:37.000Z","msg":"條友仲未訓醒"},{"pid":"e63271d4f51327e8590d507ce950214537969c2f","tid":2285380,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"兩面吹風吹民主派用法律還公義,但人大決定可以反對?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c785f2b307d33b723ab03e0dda9fae21ffac9c0d","tid":2285380,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47af7e513cc2318f20f2686320975ee116cf5749","tid":2285380,"uid":201051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,